---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Pool" description="The history of the ALCC pool, established in 1928.">
  <PageHero title="Pool" subtitle="A century-old part of the club's story." />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>ALCC Pool</h2>
      <p>Established in <strong>1928</strong>, alongside the clubhouse, the
      pool at ALCC was long a cornerstone of the club experience. For
      generations it provided a place for families to gather, with a deep
      end and diving board for the adventurous and a shallow section for
      younger swimmers. From <strong>Memorial Day to Labor Day</strong>,
      countless members enjoyed relaxing summer days by the water.</p>

      <p>In recent years, however, the pool developed a significant leak,
      ultimately leading to its closure. Safety concerns, combined with the
      escalating cost of repairs, made it impractical to reopen without
      major investment. While the American Legion Home Association has
      explored several fundraising opportunities, the necessary funds have
      not yet been secured.</p>

      <p>As a result, the pool area will be filled in at some point in the
      near future. At this time, there are no specific plans for how that
      space will be repurposed.</p>

      <p>Though it's disappointing to close a chapter that has been such a
      meaningful part of ALCC's history, the club remains committed to
      preserving and strengthening its future through thoughtful
      improvements and long-term planning.</p>

      <div class="gallery grid grid--3">
        <img src="/images/pool/pool-1.webp" alt="Historic photo of the ALCC pool" loading="lazy" />
        <img src="/images/pool/pool-2.webp" alt="Historic photo of the ALCC pool" loading="lazy" />
        <img src="/images/pool/pool-3.webp" alt="Historic photo of the ALCC pool" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <p class="caption"><em>The ALCC pool, in earlier years.</em></p>

      <a class="btn btn--red" href="/contact">Questions? Contact the Club</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .gallery { margin: 2rem 0 0.5rem; }
  .gallery img { width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 4/3; object-fit: cover; border-radius: var(--radius); }
  .caption { text-align: center; color: var(--color-gray); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
</style>
